For you, the Awareness Program is a Target List. If the company has conducted Phishing Awareness training, get the statistics: "Which department failed 60% of the time? Accounts? Sales?" Phish the people in that department. Their training has failed; you will gain entry.

In your report, you'll write: "Awareness program effectiveness evaluation failed. We phished the Accounts department with a simple invoice-themed email."

The CIA Connection
CIA means Confidentiality, Integrity, Availability

Confidentiality: Only those authorized to have access to the data can access the data.
Integrity: Only those authorized to make changes can modify the data.
Availability: Only those authorized to access data can do so when permitted.

Additional CIA Properties

Authenticity/Authentication: Verification of the identity.
Accountability: Assurance of a transaction by providing auditability.
Non-repudiation: Assurance of the transaction by proving the validity of the transaction.

